    pdf.subsection_heading("2.2", "Phase 2: Infrastructure Setup (Weeks 5-10)")
    pdf.body_text("Consultant shall: (a) provision and configure AWS and Azure environments in accordance with the approved Architecture Design; (b) implement network connectivity including VPN tunnels, Direct Connect, and ExpressRoute circuits; (c) establish identity and access management (IAM) frameworks; (d) deploy monitoring, logging, and alerting infrastructure using CloudWatch, Azure Monitor, and Datadog; (e) implement security controls including encryption, firewall rules, and compliance scanning.")
    pdf.subsection_heading("2.3", "Phase 3: Data Migration (Weeks 11-18)")
    pdf.body_text("Consultant shall: (a) execute the data migration in accordance with the approved Migration Plan, utilizing AWS Database Migration Service, Azure Data Factory, and custom ETL pipelines; (b) perform data validation and integrity checks at each stage; (c) migrate databases including Oracle, PostgreSQL, and MongoDB instances; (d) transfer unstructured data including file shares, object storage, and archival data.")
    pdf.subsection_heading("2.4", "Phase 4: Application Migration (Weeks 15-22)")
    pdf.body_text("Consultant shall: (a) migrate application workloads using a combination of lift-and-shift, re-platforming, and re-architecting strategies as identified in the Migration Plan; (b) containerize selected applications using Docker and deploy on Amazon EKS and Azure AKS; (c) reconfigure application settings, connection strings, and integrations for the cloud environment; (d) conduct performance testing and optimization.")
